{"tid":761651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來宜架賺錢咁容易","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T16:22:06.000Z","uid":27257,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee02a10ac1a87549353b9801b757e0713dce2ea","tid":761651,"uid":27257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"睇完動物展個post之後係instagram周圍碌下，㩒咗入精靈個tag到，發現有個千奇百趣嘅page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/221859_b26bb96895a75049e21e95452c052f73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F221859_b26bb96895a75049e21e95452c052f73.png&h=7e31519c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來精靈都可以買賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知可以係邊到捉？<br />\n睇下佢有咩精靈賣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222043_f60c5f96c027663c5af6cede05fe01ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222043_f60c5f96c027663c5af6cede05fe01ae.png&h=a395548e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222047_d187ce10b479509d155b957f253c5618.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222047_d187ce10b479509d155b957f253c5618.png&h=7ed7f00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喜歡和主人有身體接觸，破青啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222152_04d91a6d9c715cec98dd7a01b236528e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222152_04d91a6d9c715cec98dd7a01b236528e.png&h=d208d251&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222153_0443d56eabbddacd2d595677b06928ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222153_0443d56eabbddacd2d595677b06928ca.png&h=71702f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來真係有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我都摸精靈大波波多過佢摸我<br />\n但嚟個世界總有啲人唔信，唔知佢會點回覆呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222425_2ddbc9c26e9bc6d7ee04ad845a008d09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222425_2ddbc9c26e9bc6d7ee04ad845a008d09.png&h=23d347d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來唔信就比人開樣放上去公審，好怕怕喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222531_6196af160b0cb3d0ebd27ba589a96e2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222531_6196af160b0cb3d0ebd27ba589a96e2a.png&h=9d64ecb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/222531_548901e5ae3227439f668e5e3f2515ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F222531_548901e5ae3227439f668e5e3f2515ee.png&h=e1e36ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個留言笑到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知大家都買咩精靈呢？"},{"pid":"843b70fcffbe7526b9d3745237a89e06b3076a70","tid":761651,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"樓主自爆"},{"pid":"863964439c22324ec69cb8772d940f9025de3de2","tid":761651,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"痴西線"},{"pid":"028a7c10437a8a07a4fb48cad78e1f14b9ffd51c","tid":761651,"uid":27257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"843b70fcffbe7526b9d3745237a89e06b3076a70","tid":7